SHEETHAL SHOBAWALE:
Nikole Hannah-Jones

00:00:07.220 --> 00:00:09.430
is an award-winning,
investigative reporter

00:00:09.430 --> 00:00:12.970
covering racial injustice for
the "New York Times Magazine."

00:00:12.970 --> 00:00:14.950
She's spent the last
five years investigating

00:00:14.950 --> 00:00:18.130
how official policy
creates and maintains

00:00:18.130 --> 00:00:21.026
racial segregation in
American public schools.

00:00:21.026 --> 00:00:23.150
Nikole's reporting has won
several national awards,

00:00:23.150 --> 00:00:26.590
