00:52:36.119 --> 00:52:37.660
[LAUGHTER]

00:52:37.660 --> 00:52:40.300
You see the dog run
going at our park.

00:52:40.300 --> 00:52:42.970
Once again, always had
dogs in the community,

00:52:42.970 --> 00:52:45.220
